<h1>Shadowbanisher Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
Shadowbanisher is a Discord moderation bot.
</p>

<h2>Data we store</h2>

<p>
Shadowbanisher stores only the information needed for moderation features:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Discord user IDs</li>
<li>Discord server IDs</li>
<li>Stored roles for restoring users after a Void punishment</li>
<li>Temporary punishment end times</li>
</ul>

<h2>Why we store this data</h2>

<p>
This data is used only to provide moderation features such as temporary Void punishments and restoring roles.
</p>

<h2>Data storage</h2>

<p>
Data is stored in a local database controlled by the bot owner.
</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>

<p>
For questions about this bot, contact the bot owner.
</p>

